<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437832>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Collected specimens of Microvelia ioana (Gerromorpha, Gerridae) from Teresópolis, Rio de Janeiro (−22.4483, −43.0077) (A, B), and distribution in southeastern Brazil (C). A. Apterous male. B. Macropterous male. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
